DISCLAIMER

This guide is provided for informational purposes only. Trekking the Selvaggio
Blu is an extreme activity that carries inherent risks including serious injury
or death. Users of this guide are solely responsible for their own safety and
must assess their own skills, fitness, and equipment before attempting this trek.

The authors and contributors of this guide make no warranties about the accuracy,
completeness, or reliability of the information provided. Trail conditions,
regulations, and access may change without notice.

Always:
- Check current conditions before departure
- Register with the Municipality of Baunei
- Carry appropriate safety equipment
- Have the skills required for technical terrain
- Consider hiring a professional guide if in doubt

Respect the local environment and follow all regulations set by the Municipality
of Baunei and regional authorities.


